@startuml
!include ./plantuml-theme.puml

skinparam component<<added>> BackgroundColor #E6FFED
skinparam component<<removed>> BackgroundColor #FFECEC
skinparam component<<changed>> BackgroundColor #FFF5D6

title 架构对比（示例）

' NOTE: 必须体现 before/after、模块边界、依赖与数据路径；
'       用 <<added>>/<<removed>>/<<changed>> 标注关键变化；
'       建议突出 STEP 解析 → 三角化 → 渲染 的链路与受影响模块。

rectangle "before" {
  component [lib.rs] as A
}

rectangle "after" {
  component [lib.rs] <<changed>> as B
  ' component [predicates.rs] <<added>> as C
}

A ..[dotted].. B : 修改/重构

legend right
|= 标记 |= 含义 |
| <<added>> | 新增 |
| <<removed>> | 移除 |
| <<changed>> | 修改 |
endlegend

@enduml
